櫥櫃由義大利汽車公司Pininfarina藉由其Pininfarina Extra工業和產品設計子公司設計。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Pininfarina Partners with the Coca-Cola Company on Coca-Cola Freestyle|url=https://www.dexigner.com/news/18642|accessdate=December 22, 2011|author=Ozler|date=September 11, 2009|first=Levent|publisher=Dexigner}}</ref>涉及的技術包括微分配技術和專業的PurePour技術。本來這两種技術的發展都是為了分配精確計量的藥物。 <ref name="fastcompany1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.fastcompany.com/blog/zachary-wilson/and-how/coca-cola-gives-ten-times-choices-freestyle|title=Coca-Cola's 100-Flavor Interactive Freestyle Soda Fountain in Action|first=Zachary|author=Wilson|accessdate=May 12, 2010|date=May 10, 2010|work=Fast Company}}</ref>一個Freestyle裝置的占地面積與目前的自動販賣機類似，可以配置126種[[軟性飲料|碳酸]]和非碳酸饮料。微分配劑量將一種或多種濃縮成分掺入{{Convert|46|USfloz|L|2|abbr=on}}在飲料分配點加[[水|水]]和甜味劑的包装， <ref name="freedomblogging">{{Cite web|title=Video: Coca-Cola Freestyle Demo & How It Works|url=http://fastfood.freedomblogging.com/2009/07/21/video-coca-cola-freestyle-demo-how-it-works/29053/|accessdate=October 18, 2009|author=Luna|date=July 21, 2009|first=Nancy|work=[[Orange_County_Register|Orange County Register]]|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20130123203904/http://fastfood.freedomblogging.com/2009/07/21/video-coca-cola-freestyle-demo-how-it-works/29053/|archivedate=January 23, 2013}}</ref>因此避免使用傳统的{{Convert|5|usgal|L|1|abbr=on}}盒[[糖漿|糖浆]]（也稱为“袋中袋” ）。 <ref name="reuters">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/rbssConsumerGoodsAndRetailNews/idUSN2915883820090929|title=Coca-Cola to Expand Testing of New Drink Fountain|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|accessdate=October 18, 2009|date=September 30, 2009|first=Matthew|author=Bigg}}</ref>藥筒將濃縮的食材存儲在分配櫃中，並且起用了[[射频识别|RFID]] 。該機器使用RFID芯片來檢測其耗材，並向其他設備廣播補给的需求。這些機器将將[[供给和需求|供需]]數據傳送到可口可樂和所有者，包括出售的[[品牌|品牌]]，銷售日期，[[排错|故障排除]]信息和服務數據。 <ref name="bsquare">{{Cite news|url=http://atlanta.bizjournals.com/atlanta/othercities/seattle/stories/2009/07/20/daily8.html?s=industry|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911220709/http://atlanta.bizjournals.com/atlanta/othercities/seattle/stories/2009/07/20/daily8.html?s=industry|archivedate=September 11, 2016|title=Bsquare-Coca-Cola Team Up on High-Tech Soda Machine|work=Puget Sound Business Journal|date=July 20, 2009|accessdate=August 25, 2009|location=Seattle}}</ref>保留了傳统的[[食用冰塊|冰塊]]分配器。 <ref name="ajc1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.ajc.com/business/coke-targets-freestyle-expansion-149759.html|title=Coke Targets Freestyle Expansion for 2010|first=Joe Guy|author=Collier|work=[[The_Atlanta_Journal-Constitution|The Atlanta Journal-Constitution]]|date=September 29, 2009|accessdate=October 18, 2009}}</ref>

== 歷史發展 ==
測試在2009年7月在猶他州， <ref name="fastcompany1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.fastcompany.com/blog/zachary-wilson/and-how/coca-cola-gives-ten-times-choices-freestyle|title=Coca-Cola's 100-Flavor Interactive Freestyle Soda Fountain in Action|first=Zachary|author=Wilson|accessdate=May 12, 2010|date=May 10, 2010|work=Fast Company}}</ref>南加州， <ref name="freedomblogging">{{Cite web|title=Video: Coca-Cola Freestyle Demo & How It Works|url=http://fastfood.freedomblogging.com/2009/07/21/video-coca-cola-freestyle-demo-how-it-works/29053/|accessdate=October 18, 2009|author=Luna|date=July 21, 2009|first=Nancy|work=[[Orange_County_Register|Orange County Register]]|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20130123203904/http://fastfood.freedomblogging.com/2009/07/21/video-coca-cola-freestyle-demo-how-it-works/29053/|archivedate=January 23, 2013}}</ref><ref name="ajc1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.ajc.com/business/coke-targets-freestyle-expansion-149759.html|title=Coke Targets Freestyle Expansion for 2010|first=Joe Guy|author=Collier|work=[[The_Atlanta_Journal-Constitution|The Atlanta Journal-Constitution]]|date=September 29, 2009|accessdate=October 18, 2009}}</ref>和喬治亞州開始，直到夏天结束時在美國各地已建立60多個據點。 <ref name="KGO Freestyle">{{Cite news|url=http://abclocal.go.com/kgo/story?section=news/bizarre&id=6927931|title=New Soda Machines Customizes Flavors|date=July 22, 2009|location=San Francisco|publisher=[[KGO-TV|KGO-TV]]|accessdate=October 18, 2009|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604050330/http://abclocal.go.com/kgo/story?section=news%2Fbizarre&id=6927931|archivedate=June 4, 2011}}</ref>可口可樂的來源地亞特蘭大附近的測試地點包括可口可樂世界， AMC劇院Southlake Pavilion 24和Parkway Point 15  <ref>{{Cite web|title=Event @ AMC|url=http://www.facebook.com/album.php?aid=126176&id=106593592062&ref=mf|accessdate=October 18, 2009|date=October 2, 2009|publisher=The Coca-Cola Company}}</ref>以及區域食物連鎖，包括Willy's Mexicana Grill。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=More Flavors of Coke Coming to a Restaurant Near You|url=http://www.11alive.com/rss/rss_story.aspx?storyid=135920|accessdate=May 13, 2010|author=Sweigart|date=October 2, 2009|first=Christ|format=Video|publisher=[[WXIA-TV|WXIA-TV]]|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20121203024138/http://www.11alive.com/rss/rss_story.aspx?storyid=135920|archivedate=December 3, 2012}}</ref>佛羅里旯環球影城和冒險島主题公園以及佛羅里達州布埃纳维斯塔湖的迪士尼之泉購物商場温泉的AMC電影院和在埃德蒙顿的艾伯塔省西埃德蒙頓購物中心的世界水上樂園以及艾伯塔省的和在喬治亞州瓦爾多斯塔的Wild Adventures提供三台機器。 

